snippet.textDisplay: Alot of comments keep saying things about the singers, or how one is better than the other... over and over. I don't understand. Is there some kind of rivalry? I thought they both did an amazing job. The amount of control it takes to fluctuate your voice over many notes, but still only using few syllables... I am amazed. I want to learn this from your culture. Such beauty... that is why I am surprised to see people say things about the girl singer against the guy singer, or vise versa. They were both amazing
